Message API methods:
GET /message/new/:id
    get the message sorted by date sent if you are the receiver. The admin has no premission to view private messages.
POST /message/new/:id
     create a new message to the receiver with :id
     form data headers:
     messageTitle message 
GET /sent/
     check the messages you sent sorted by date.  Uses req to get the informations.
GET /update/
    used to check how many new messages a particular user has.  constantly request this to keep updated.
POST /update/:id
    read the message with :id.  This will register in the databse as read and will not show up as a new message